WEBVTT

01:32.070 --> 01:34.930
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:37.970
[Episode 32]

01:41.710 --> 01:42.350
Your Highness, watch out!

01:42.350 --> 01:43.210
Your Highness!

01:44.560 --> 01:45.420
What happened?

01:45.840 --> 01:46.780
That mute girl is from Qiang State.

01:46.780 --> 01:48.310
She poisoned Her Highness.

01:48.350 --> 01:49.120
Summon the imperial physician!

01:49.120 --> 01:49.479
No.

01:50.120 --> 01:50.590
Bai.

01:51.280 --> 01:52.210
Do you remember?

01:52.840 --> 01:53.970
When two stars meet,

01:54.039 --> 01:55.370
one is destined to fall.

01:55.759 --> 01:56.960
If one of us

01:56.979 --> 01:58.200
must die

01:59.150 --> 02:00.630
for the other to live,

02:01.560 --> 02:02.760
that the survivor...

02:03.280 --> 02:04.690
doesn't have to be me.

02:05.760 --> 02:06.690
You want to trade

02:08.240 --> 02:09.240
your life for his?

02:13.190 --> 02:13.990
No, you can't.

02:14.150 --> 02:15.280
I've made up my mind.

02:15.440 --> 02:16.970
Stop trying to persuade me.

02:17.620 --> 02:18.390
Leave us.

02:19.400 --> 02:19.910
Your Highness.

02:19.910 --> 02:21.840
-Your Highness.
-Allow us to have our final moments.

02:21.840 --> 02:22.400
Leave!

02:23.630 --> 02:24.030
Yes.

02:30.400 --> 02:30.930
Let's go.

02:40.560 --> 02:41.190
CEO Dan,

02:43.050 --> 02:44.110
I broke my promise.

02:46.840 --> 02:48.900
I don't want to wait for the next life,

02:50.310 --> 02:51.910
so you can't leave me either.

03:34.680 --> 03:35.540
Your Highness.

03:42.610 --> 03:43.540
Thank goodness.

03:43.630 --> 03:44.890
You're finally awake.

03:50.120 --> 03:51.120
How come I'm fine?

03:54.470 --> 03:54.870
You...

03:55.870 --> 03:56.930
What did you all do?

03:58.960 --> 04:00.220
We didn't do anything.

04:00.680 --> 04:01.810
Physician Xiao came

04:01.910 --> 04:03.170
to check on your pulse.

04:03.400 --> 04:04.960
The poison's effect only lasts a night.

04:04.960 --> 04:05.850
So now,

04:06.080 --> 04:07.410
you are basically fine.

04:10.280 --> 04:11.050
So...

04:12.520 --> 04:14.380
Flower never intended to kill me.

04:15.000 --> 04:17.399
She only wanted to
threaten me with poison.

04:18.240 --> 04:18.899
It seems so.

04:20.899 --> 04:22.230
What about His Majesty?

04:22.430 --> 04:23.720
What did Physician Xiao say?

04:23.720 --> 04:24.580
His Majesty...

04:26.390 --> 04:27.420
is still in a coma.

04:28.600 --> 04:29.460
Your Highness!

04:30.190 --> 04:31.590
Your Highness! Bad news!

04:32.870 --> 04:34.670
The mute girl poisoned herself!

04:36.220 --> 04:37.570
[Zhaoyang Palace]

04:39.700 --> 04:40.970
We deserve to die.

04:41.240 --> 04:42.530
She had poison hidden with her.

04:42.530 --> 04:44.120
We were negligent for a moment,

04:44.120 --> 04:44.390
and she...

04:44.390 --> 04:45.390
I don't blame you.

04:45.470 --> 04:47.920
We should be blaming those
who gave her orders instead.

04:47.920 --> 04:49.780
They wouldn't even spare a child.

04:50.390 --> 04:51.250
I'll go see her.

04:54.000 --> 04:54.760
Flower!

05:01.430 --> 05:02.050
Flower.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.310
Can you tell me

05:03.310 --> 05:04.320
what poison did you take?

05:04.320 --> 05:05.850
We'll find a way to save you.

05:08.560 --> 05:10.090
Poison from Qiang State...

05:11.560 --> 05:12.360
has no cure.

05:13.110 --> 05:14.470
You silly child.

05:15.120 --> 05:16.890
You knew there were
so many secret guards in the palace.

05:16.890 --> 05:18.620
You knew you wouldn't succeed.

05:18.800 --> 05:20.160
Why did you still do it?

05:21.750 --> 05:23.810
If the Emperor were to die of illness,

05:25.740 --> 05:27.380
you would become Great Xia's

05:28.360 --> 05:29.630
highest noble.

05:31.310 --> 05:32.550
To get revenge,

05:33.510 --> 05:35.320
I would have to kill you.

05:36.480 --> 05:38.010
But I couldn't bear to do it.

05:43.450 --> 05:44.050
So...

05:46.180 --> 05:47.630
you did this on purpose?

05:50.080 --> 05:51.350
All of them said...

05:53.000 --> 05:53.930
the people of Xia

05:54.720 --> 05:56.200
are all bad.

05:58.600 --> 05:59.680
They also said

06:01.390 --> 06:04.090
as long as I become the queen's warrior,

06:04.750 --> 06:06.410
I could reunite with my family

06:07.480 --> 06:09.070
in heaven.

06:07.730 --> 06:10.410
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

06:10.950 --> 06:11.640
But...

06:11.170 --> 06:14.180
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

06:13.870 --> 06:14.720
But...

06:14.970 --> 06:18.170
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

06:15.960 --> 06:16.840
But what?

06:21.290 --> 06:23.980
♪ Then we transform ♪

06:24.720 --> 06:27.780
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

06:28.160 --> 06:32.790
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

06:30.330 --> 06:31.150
But...

06:32.630 --> 06:34.270
you remind me of my sister.

06:33.659 --> 06:36.000
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

06:36.820 --> 06:39.430
♪ And let time freeze ♪

06:38.909 --> 06:39.800
Easy, Chu Wu.

06:39.960 --> 06:40.850
She's just a child.

06:40.140 --> 06:45.870
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

06:41.360 --> 06:42.250
The soldiers are here.

06:42.250 --> 06:43.159
You should run.

06:43.370 --> 06:44.570
Don't steal anymore.

06:46.270 --> 06:47.560
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

06:46.980 --> 06:47.909
Don't be afraid.

06:48.240 --> 06:51.090
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

06:48.360 --> 06:49.490
I'll give you a name.

06:50.120 --> 06:51.120
Let's call you...

06:51.270 --> 06:52.310
Flower. How's that?

06:51.620 --> 06:53.300
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

06:53.320 --> 06:59.210
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

06:59.760 --> 07:01.220
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

07:01.690 --> 07:04.600
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

07:05.070 --> 07:07.210
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

07:07.310 --> 07:08.840
♪ We can dance together ♪

07:08.860 --> 07:18.460
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

07:19.680 --> 07:20.310
Sister.

07:24.600 --> 07:26.420
My mom is here to pick me up.

07:28.500 --> 07:30.030
I'm going home.

07:41.170 --> 07:43.700
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

07:44.620 --> 07:47.040
♪ And let time freeze ♪

07:47.750 --> 07:53.520
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

07:53.560 --> 07:54.140
Flower?

07:53.880 --> 07:55.070
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

07:55.810 --> 07:58.570
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

07:57.240 --> 07:57.750
Flower!

07:59.220 --> 08:00.790
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

07:59.680 --> 08:00.310
Flower!

08:00.810 --> 08:06.770
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

08:07.450 --> 08:08.620
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

08:09.280 --> 08:12.250
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

08:12.730 --> 08:14.840
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

08:14.890 --> 08:16.410
♪ We can dance together ♪

08:16.470 --> 08:25.450
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

08:27.230 --> 08:33.280
♪ Never looking back ♪

08:49.750 --> 08:50.750
I have ordered men

08:51.270 --> 08:53.200
to bury the child outside the city.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.790
We will just tell the rest

08:54.910 --> 08:56.510
that she has left the palace.

08:59.550 --> 09:01.750
Your Highness,
please do not grieve too deeply.

09:01.750 --> 09:03.480
You must take care of yourself.

09:04.240 --> 09:05.370
Right now, everyone

09:05.720 --> 09:07.650
is counting on you, Your Highness.

09:08.510 --> 09:09.030
Bai.

09:10.790 --> 09:11.590
You know what?

09:15.270 --> 09:16.840
Since I came to this world,

09:20.000 --> 09:21.120
people like Xu Yao

09:22.550 --> 09:23.150
and Du Shan

09:23.790 --> 09:24.720
were all killed.

09:25.630 --> 09:27.090
Then Mei took her own life,

09:28.270 --> 09:30.330
while Wang Zhao died for our country.

09:30.480 --> 09:32.340
Later, Yong'er died tragically,

09:33.390 --> 09:35.190
and Cen Jintian died of illness.

09:37.120 --> 09:38.720
Mr. Bei had also passed away.

09:40.590 --> 09:42.110
And now even Flower...

09:44.120 --> 09:45.180
had died of poison.

09:47.330 --> 09:48.460
All the people I love

09:50.480 --> 09:51.790
and cherish

09:55.290 --> 09:56.700
is leaving me.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.400
If His Majesty too...

10:06.720 --> 10:08.780
I wouldn't be able to hold on anymore.

10:12.790 --> 10:13.650
Your Highness.

10:15.270 --> 10:16.080
My Master said

10:16.680 --> 10:18.210
he was sure I could help him.

10:20.250 --> 10:21.470
He wouldn't be wrong.

10:26.330 --> 10:27.060
I hope so.

10:47.550 --> 10:48.480
Physician Xiao.

10:49.720 --> 10:50.450
General Lin.

10:51.480 --> 10:52.630
Has there been any new discovery regarding

10:52.630 --> 10:54.480
the poison Her Highness had sent?

10:54.480 --> 10:56.480
I applied the poison to a mouse's wound,

10:56.480 --> 10:58.360
and the wound wouldn't heal
for a long time.

10:58.360 --> 10:59.870
This effect is very similar to the poison

10:59.870 --> 11:01.510
Tu'er used on his blade before.

11:01.510 --> 11:02.910
It's just that the dosage is too low.

11:02.910 --> 11:05.040
I was about to ask where you got it from.

11:07.870 --> 11:08.870
The mute girl serving Her Highness

11:08.870 --> 11:10.480
left this flower before she died.

11:10.480 --> 11:11.140
I wonder...

11:11.600 --> 11:13.860
if it has anything to do with this poison.

11:28.320 --> 11:28.780
It does!

11:29.770 --> 11:30.520
Great.

11:31.320 --> 11:32.010
I'll get a painter

11:32.010 --> 11:32.780
to copy it.

11:33.750 --> 11:34.870
I'll dig to the ends of the earth

11:34.870 --> 11:35.700
to find it.

11:35.990 --> 11:36.720
General Lin.

11:39.750 --> 11:40.620
I think...

11:42.320 --> 11:43.980
I've seen this flower before.

11:46.570 --> 11:48.170
I heard you guys found a clue?

11:50.320 --> 11:51.450
Physician Xiao said

11:51.590 --> 11:54.000
he saw someone growing
this flower in the flower house.

11:54.000 --> 11:56.550
This might be the key to curing
His Majesty's poison.

11:56.550 --> 11:57.080
Found it!

11:57.600 --> 11:58.130
Found it!

12:05.550 --> 12:07.000
It was originally planted in the ground.

12:07.000 --> 12:09.200
But perhaps the Imperial Medical Bureau
needed to plant other herbs,

12:09.200 --> 12:10.530
so they moved it to a pot.

12:10.880 --> 12:11.960
That's why we couldn't find it right away.

12:11.960 --> 12:13.390
It matches these dried flowers.

12:13.390 --> 12:14.520
No mistake about it.

12:15.240 --> 12:16.300
But in this palace,

12:17.150 --> 12:17.790
who else

12:18.310 --> 12:20.370
would grow flowers from Qiang State?

12:20.750 --> 12:21.440
It's...

12:22.510 --> 12:23.360
Consort Xie.

12:24.150 --> 12:26.350
I've loved gardening since I was young.

12:26.480 --> 12:28.240
I saw these in
the Empress Dowager's garden.

12:28.240 --> 12:29.740
These are so rare,

12:30.320 --> 12:32.030
so I thought I'd ask for a few sprigs.

12:32.030 --> 12:33.350
These plants

12:33.440 --> 12:35.900
were rare tributes from various countries.

12:36.060 --> 12:37.170
Consort Xie,

12:37.750 --> 12:38.880
you have good taste.

12:57.040 --> 12:57.900
Your Highness.

12:58.510 --> 12:59.440
Physician Xiao,

12:59.960 --> 13:01.150
you came just at the right time.

13:01.150 --> 13:02.670
Could you take a look at this flower

13:02.670 --> 13:04.600
and tell me the best way to plant it?

13:06.120 --> 13:06.780
Be careful.

13:08.440 --> 13:09.340
Thick roots,

13:09.960 --> 13:10.890
slender leaves,

13:12.270 --> 13:13.730
and bell-shaped flowers.

13:14.220 --> 13:16.660
It grows well in damp, miasmic places,

13:17.030 --> 13:19.000
and doesn't seem to be from our Great Xia.

13:19.000 --> 13:21.030
You have a sharp eye, Physician Xiao.

13:21.030 --> 13:23.840
These are flowers presented to the Empress Dowager
as tribute from foreign lands.

13:23.840 --> 13:25.500
I remember Consort Xie saying

13:26.150 --> 13:28.910
that she received this as a reward
from the Empress Dowager.

13:28.910 --> 13:31.110
Now that you mention it, it rings a bell.

13:31.390 --> 13:33.250
Before the Empress Dowager died,

13:33.790 --> 13:35.920
she seemed to have made such a gesture.

13:38.480 --> 13:41.340
It's exactly the same gesture
Flower made just now.

13:41.630 --> 13:42.760
This is a gesture...

13:42.870 --> 13:45.240
made by people of Qiang State to
pray for their souls to return home.

13:45.240 --> 13:47.570
The Empress Dowager was from Qiang State?

13:48.920 --> 13:49.700
No wonder.

13:50.870 --> 13:52.430
She hated the late Emperor so much,

13:52.430 --> 13:53.830
yet she spared no cost

13:53.960 --> 13:55.030
to manipulate the court

13:55.030 --> 13:56.630
and bring chaos to Great Xia.

13:57.510 --> 13:59.570
It turns out she was just like Flower,

13:59.910 --> 14:01.370
both pawns of Qiang State.

14:03.240 --> 14:04.100
Your Highness.

14:04.840 --> 14:07.120
For the method of fighting poison
with poison, which we had discussed,

14:07.120 --> 14:08.450
the missing ingredient

14:09.670 --> 14:11.400
might be this plant right here.

14:19.320 --> 14:19.850
Yong'er.

14:21.790 --> 14:23.450
You really are the chosen one.

14:25.350 --> 14:26.560
This last hope...

14:29.030 --> 14:30.560
has been with you all along.

14:38.910 --> 14:39.770
Your Highness,

14:40.180 --> 14:41.500
I have replicated it according to
the ancient formula.

14:41.500 --> 14:43.760
You just have to sprinkle it on the wound.

14:46.090 --> 14:47.150
Are you confident?

14:47.720 --> 14:48.750
Previously, when His Majesty

14:48.750 --> 14:49.950
was stabbed by Tu'er,

14:50.790 --> 14:52.320
not only did the wound heal,

14:52.600 --> 14:54.730
but his headaches were also relieved.

14:54.870 --> 14:56.790
This method of fighting poison with poison

14:56.790 --> 14:58.390
should theoretically work,

14:59.320 --> 15:01.120
but no one has actually tried it.

15:02.550 --> 15:05.280
When in doubt between
advancing and retreating,

15:05.500 --> 15:07.160
one should choose to advance.

16:07.390 --> 16:08.050
He's awake.

16:12.670 --> 16:13.320
Wanyin.

16:14.550 --> 16:15.080
I'm here.

16:18.750 --> 16:19.550
How are you?

16:23.310 --> 16:23.720
Fine.

16:23.720 --> 16:24.360
Thank you.

16:25.120 --> 16:25.670
And you?

16:39.440 --> 16:41.670
It's been 197 days.

16:42.870 --> 16:44.000
That's half a year.

16:44.840 --> 16:47.200
I wonder how things are outside.

16:54.440 --> 16:55.300
Your Highness.

17:02.360 --> 17:03.720
You are...

17:05.109 --> 17:07.109
It's me, Wu Jiadong, Your Highness.

17:10.440 --> 17:12.130
How did you get in?

17:12.960 --> 17:13.819
Your Highness,

17:15.589 --> 17:16.589
I am incompetent.

17:17.160 --> 17:18.020
The guards here

17:18.060 --> 17:19.190
are incorruptible.

17:20.160 --> 17:21.690
I waited for half a year,

17:22.069 --> 17:24.020
until chaos broke out outside

17:24.160 --> 17:25.310
and people's resolve wavered.

17:25.310 --> 17:26.960
Only then could I bribe my way through

17:26.960 --> 17:27.960
to sneak inside

17:28.240 --> 17:29.500
and see Your Highness.

17:31.880 --> 17:33.080
Keep your voice down.

17:34.790 --> 17:35.850
Don't you think...

17:38.440 --> 17:40.880
there are eyes everywhere watching me?

17:41.880 --> 17:44.210
-Your Highness. You...
-My every move...

17:45.000 --> 17:46.640
is controlled by him.

17:50.920 --> 17:51.590
Come on.

17:53.070 --> 17:53.400
Here.

17:54.400 --> 17:55.380
Look at this.

17:56.160 --> 17:57.040
Sometimes...

17:58.940 --> 18:00.770
the chess piece I place here

18:01.480 --> 18:03.080
ends up somewhere else.

18:04.000 --> 18:04.520
And...

18:05.240 --> 18:06.760
the guards at the door,

18:08.310 --> 18:10.000
they never change.

18:12.150 --> 18:13.880
It's as if they have no friends,

18:15.070 --> 18:15.880
no family,

18:17.300 --> 18:18.560
and nothing else to do.

18:20.200 --> 18:21.480
Their life's mission

18:22.440 --> 18:24.510
seems to be just guarding me.

18:28.790 --> 18:29.830
Sometimes,

18:32.150 --> 18:33.410
in a haze of confusion,

18:35.040 --> 18:38.390
I can still hear them
calling me Worthy Lord.

18:41.030 --> 18:42.590
It's as if my life

18:43.550 --> 18:45.140
has different versions.

18:47.480 --> 18:48.270
One time,

18:49.710 --> 18:51.830
they hailed 'Long live the Emperor.'

18:53.640 --> 18:56.260
I managed Great Xia perfectly fine,

18:56.720 --> 18:58.520
bringing peace and prosperity.

19:00.680 --> 19:03.140
They all called me the true Son of Heaven.

19:07.160 --> 19:09.870
There is an invisible hand in this world,

19:11.830 --> 19:13.620
and we are all his pawns.

19:18.720 --> 19:20.780
You certainly wouldn't understand,

19:22.170 --> 19:24.060
because you are a level below me.

19:24.160 --> 19:24.730
Yes.

19:28.350 --> 19:29.970
I'll show you right now.

19:33.270 --> 19:33.920
It's time.

19:35.000 --> 19:37.130
Someone will interrupt us any moment.

19:41.070 --> 19:42.330
The guards are coming.

19:42.960 --> 19:43.740
I must go.

19:48.350 --> 19:49.590
Interesting.

19:55.040 --> 19:55.900
Your Highness,

19:56.140 --> 19:58.350
please take care.

19:58.750 --> 20:00.870
You just have to wait a little longer,

20:01.100 --> 20:03.600
and you will rise to power again.

20:04.200 --> 20:05.680
I'll take my leave.

20:08.750 --> 20:10.200
Interesting.

20:19.830 --> 20:22.480
You guys don't seem to be much good.

20:26.320 --> 20:27.950
I've got you!

20:35.680 --> 20:37.240
I've got you!

20:38.270 --> 20:39.070
Your Majesty,

20:39.160 --> 20:41.090
Xiahou Bo actually believed it.

20:41.150 --> 20:42.160
When I left,

20:42.400 --> 20:44.480
he was still shouting that
he is the true...

20:44.480 --> 20:45.610
the true... true...

20:46.400 --> 20:47.860
What utter nonsense!

20:49.590 --> 20:51.020
From now on, go see him

20:51.310 --> 20:52.370
every now and then.

20:53.070 --> 20:54.060
Tell him

20:54.480 --> 20:56.340
how chaotic the world outside is.

20:56.460 --> 20:57.340
Make him wait.

20:59.070 --> 21:00.130
As long as he lives,

21:00.920 --> 21:02.590
I won't hold you accountable.

21:03.070 --> 21:04.310
Thank you, Your Majesty,

21:04.310 --> 21:06.580
for giving me a chance to redeem myself.

21:07.170 --> 21:08.090
You may leave.

21:08.510 --> 21:09.910
Thank you, Your Majesty.

21:19.350 --> 21:20.440
Speak your mind.

21:22.540 --> 21:23.980
I don't understand.

21:24.200 --> 21:26.260
Why are you doing this, Your Majesty?

21:28.050 --> 21:29.380
As long as there is hope,

21:29.510 --> 21:30.710
one won't seek death.

21:31.110 --> 21:33.400
But Prince Duan committed treason first.

21:33.400 --> 21:34.640
We are still brothers,

21:34.640 --> 21:35.640
actual brothers.

21:37.720 --> 21:38.520
Your Majesty,

21:39.870 --> 21:41.900
you are truly benevolent.

21:42.160 --> 21:44.090
Don't force tears if you have none.

21:48.680 --> 21:49.800
When did Wanyin leave the palace?

21:49.800 --> 21:51.060
Why isn't she back yet?

21:51.880 --> 21:53.900
Her Highness left only an hour ago.

21:54.400 --> 21:56.200
That's too long. I'll go get her.

21:56.350 --> 21:56.720
Yes.

21:59.590 --> 22:00.650
Don't come with me.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.220
Prepare hotpot for me.

22:03.240 --> 22:04.440
We'll have the nine-grid pot tonight.

22:04.440 --> 22:05.370
Yes.

22:08.030 --> 22:09.160
-Stop!
-Slow down.

22:09.670 --> 22:10.400
Here, Er Lan.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.900
Thank you, Your Highness.

22:17.880 --> 22:18.610
Brother Cen.

22:19.030 --> 22:20.280
Because of your Yan millet,

22:20.280 --> 22:22.080
Great Xia survived the drought.

22:23.070 --> 22:24.040
Now,

22:24.110 --> 22:25.840
the war in Yan State has been quelled.

22:25.080 --> 22:28.790
[Tomb of Wang Zhao]

22:26.070 --> 22:27.790
Tu'er has become the Emperor of Yan,

22:27.790 --> 22:29.110
and had even sent a treaty of alliance.

22:28.850 --> 22:31.470
[Tomb of Du Shan]

22:29.830 --> 22:31.720
An era of peace and prosperity
has arrived.

22:31.720 --> 22:33.250
With you here, Brother Cen,

22:33.350 --> 22:35.680
we will see abundant harvests every year.

22:36.590 --> 22:37.020
Slow down.

22:37.020 --> 22:38.020
Let's take a walk.

22:39.310 --> 22:39.680
Okay.

22:40.550 --> 22:43.080
-Be careful not to fall.
-Let’s go over there.

22:44.270 --> 22:46.240
Li Yunxi has been watching you
for quite a while now.

22:46.240 --> 22:48.440
He even asked me about you a few days ago.

22:50.200 --> 22:51.830
Are you trying to set us up,
Your Highness?

22:51.830 --> 22:53.090
I wouldn't go that far.

22:53.790 --> 22:55.560
What kind of life you want,

22:55.790 --> 22:57.250
and who you want to be with,

22:57.470 --> 22:58.600
is all up to you.

23:03.280 --> 23:04.610
What's on your mind now?

23:05.030 --> 23:06.490
Do you still want to leave?

23:08.010 --> 23:09.720
Now that the imperial examinations
have resumed,

23:09.720 --> 23:11.210
talented people are emerging in court.

23:11.210 --> 23:12.370
My departure now

23:12.720 --> 23:14.200
can be seen as a graceful exit.

23:14.200 --> 23:15.000
Look, look!

23:15.000 --> 23:16.030
It's just...

23:19.240 --> 23:21.900
I'm just a bit worried about you,
Your Highness.

23:22.000 --> 23:23.590
After all, joint rule by
the emperor and empress

23:23.590 --> 23:25.320
will inevitably cause gossip.

23:26.510 --> 23:27.790
Your Highness' influence is at its peak,

23:27.790 --> 23:29.590
so no one dares to challenge you.

23:29.880 --> 23:32.680
But from now on, you'll be swamped with
daily affairs and countless tasks,

23:32.680 --> 23:33.200
and even just a small mistake—

23:33.200 --> 23:35.400
It doesn't matter if mistakes are made.

23:40.400 --> 23:42.530
Achievements belong to Her Highness,

23:42.590 --> 23:44.520
while any minor mistakes are mine.

23:44.550 --> 23:46.310
When loyal ministers offer counsel,

23:46.310 --> 23:48.170
Her Highness will surely listen.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.160
But...

23:50.070 --> 23:52.480
If any treacherous schemers
seek to exploit the situation,

23:52.480 --> 23:53.330
my madness

23:53.830 --> 23:55.390
can relapse at any time.

23:56.070 --> 23:57.270
I might accidentally

23:57.640 --> 23:59.400
kill someone in court again.

23:59.990 --> 24:01.940
You really know how to play along.

24:03.830 --> 24:04.660
Greetings, Your Majesty.

24:04.660 --> 24:05.140
Rise.

24:06.270 --> 24:07.020
Alright.

24:07.200 --> 24:08.480
Go back to the carriage and
stay out of the wind.

24:08.480 --> 24:09.590
We're not done talking yet.

24:09.590 --> 24:10.540
Let me listen in.

24:10.670 --> 24:11.760
Go. Stop fussing.

24:14.310 --> 24:15.640
Okay, I'll go find them.

24:26.110 --> 24:26.870
To be honest,

24:27.890 --> 24:29.690
I can't bear to let you go either.

24:30.840 --> 24:34.230
[Tomb of Wang Zhao]

24:31.000 --> 24:32.680
Now that Li Yunxi and Yang Duojie

24:32.680 --> 24:34.190
are doing so well,

24:34.570 --> 24:36.300
are you willing to lose to them?

24:36.680 --> 24:37.640
But now,

24:37.710 --> 24:39.450
everyone knows I am a woman,

24:39.640 --> 24:42.070
and there is no precedent
for female officials.

24:42.070 --> 24:43.240
There was never a precedent

24:43.240 --> 24:45.310
for joint rule by both
the emperor and empress either.

24:45.310 --> 24:46.240
For many things,

24:46.400 --> 24:47.260
if we don't try,

24:47.590 --> 24:49.450
how could there be any precedent?

24:49.640 --> 24:50.040
Er Lan.

24:50.810 --> 24:52.610
Precisely because we are women,

24:53.510 --> 24:54.950
we must remember.

24:55.350 --> 24:56.280
For many things,

24:57.550 --> 24:59.470
we should be the first to do them,

24:59.930 --> 25:01.280
not the last.

25:05.560 --> 25:07.490
Li Yunxi was wrong about one thing.

25:08.110 --> 25:09.720
He's not the only one in this world

25:09.720 --> 25:10.920
who understands you.

25:13.750 --> 25:16.910
With the great ambitions of yours
to make your mark in history,

25:16.910 --> 25:18.970
why hide behind someone else's name?

25:20.030 --> 25:20.780
We women

25:21.750 --> 25:23.680
can also achieve great things that

25:24.030 --> 25:25.560
benefit the common people.

25:30.390 --> 25:31.250
Your Highness.

25:34.640 --> 25:35.300
Go and play.

25:37.780 --> 25:38.220
Also,

25:38.940 --> 25:40.480
I am currently short-handed on my mission

25:40.480 --> 25:43.030
to establish girls' schools
across the country.

25:43.030 --> 25:43.830
In the future,

25:43.960 --> 25:45.160
little girls like her

25:45.400 --> 25:47.260
can attend school just like boys.

25:47.590 --> 25:48.050
Er Lan.

25:48.830 --> 25:50.560
What do you think of this offer?

25:51.070 --> 25:52.200
Aren't you tempted?

25:57.920 --> 25:58.980
You are truly wise.

25:58.990 --> 25:59.920
You know right away

25:59.920 --> 26:00.960
if it'll work or not.

26:00.960 --> 26:01.750
Of course.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.880
Did you catch a chill?

26:07.960 --> 26:09.420
Why are your hands so cold?

26:15.730 --> 26:18.130
Don't frown on such a
beautiful spring day.

26:19.400 --> 26:21.110
Didn't Physician Xiao mention that

26:21.110 --> 26:22.240
the poison in my body

26:22.370 --> 26:23.770
has been mostly cleared?

26:26.130 --> 26:27.160
Don't worry.

26:27.750 --> 26:29.880
I will be with you for many, many years.

26:32.630 --> 26:33.810
I told you to go back and wait.

26:33.810 --> 26:35.810
Couldn't you wait just for a moment?

26:36.720 --> 26:38.650
I'll go back and drink ginger soup.

26:39.310 --> 26:40.440
That's more like it.

26:43.590 --> 26:45.720
I don't want to live like that anymore—

26:46.030 --> 26:47.160
alone in the palace,

26:48.200 --> 26:50.530
living in fear and dread, waiting for you.

26:58.350 --> 27:01.240
When one hears the woeful tune of
"Breaking the Willow Branch",

27:01.240 --> 27:03.640
who wouldn't feel homesick?

27:05.030 --> 27:06.200
Wherever you are

27:07.490 --> 27:09.190
is my home.

27:11.070 --> 27:12.590
Don't say such cheesy pickup lines

27:12.590 --> 27:13.760
from now on.

27:17.780 --> 27:19.050
I meant in the future.

27:20.510 --> 27:23.550
But today, I suppose I could make myself
listen some more.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.680
Then I'll continue.

27:26.270 --> 27:27.420
As for the future,

27:27.640 --> 27:29.460
let's set a small goal first.

27:29.570 --> 27:30.900
Let's earn 100 million.

27:31.310 --> 27:33.000
We'll then find an experienced driver

27:33.000 --> 27:33.610
to take us

27:34.030 --> 27:35.560
to travel around the world.

27:38.310 --> 27:39.270
Your Majesty,

27:39.640 --> 27:40.590
once we leave,

27:40.680 --> 27:43.160
there's no one left
to play shuttlecock with you.

27:43.160 --> 27:44.960
I will miss you all too.

27:45.680 --> 27:48.240
But His Majesty insists on
disbanding the harem.

27:48.240 --> 27:49.570
I tried to persuade him,

27:49.640 --> 27:50.980
but his mind is made up.

27:51.160 --> 27:52.560
There's nothing I can do.

27:53.310 --> 27:55.200
We are not blessed with the good fortune

27:55.200 --> 27:57.020
to serve His Majesty

27:57.240 --> 27:58.650
and live and die with him.

28:00.110 --> 28:02.720
You really want to live and die
with His Majesty?

28:02.720 --> 28:03.720
Then how about...

28:04.030 --> 28:05.890
I go plead with His Majesty again?

28:06.240 --> 28:07.270
-No, no, no.
-No, no, no.

28:07.270 --> 28:09.800
That's really not necessary,
Your Highness.

28:11.790 --> 28:12.960
After you leave the palace,

28:12.960 --> 28:13.790
what do you all want to do?

28:13.790 --> 28:15.110
Go home first, of course.

28:15.110 --> 28:17.910
My parents were thrilled to hear
I was coming home.

28:18.070 --> 28:19.830
You still have a home to return to.

28:19.830 --> 28:20.440
As for me,

28:21.300 --> 28:23.700
I'll just have to find
another man to marry.

28:25.440 --> 28:27.270
What's wrong with getting married?

28:27.270 --> 28:29.780
This time, I'll find someone I like.

28:30.110 --> 28:31.870
I want to have a real romance.

28:33.510 --> 28:34.930
Sister, do you mean

28:35.030 --> 28:36.780
you never liked His Majesty?

28:41.420 --> 28:43.020
The money His Majesty gave me

28:43.070 --> 28:45.340
is enough to open a shop in the capital.

28:45.960 --> 28:47.830
I want to sell my rose essence.

28:48.160 --> 28:50.440
My secret recipe will
surely make a fortune.

28:50.440 --> 28:51.350
When the time comes,

28:51.350 --> 28:53.280
all of you must come and support me.

28:54.000 --> 28:54.510
Sure!

28:55.440 --> 28:55.980
Alright.

28:56.720 --> 28:58.840
No matter what you choose,

28:59.350 --> 29:00.610
I hope that from now on,

29:00.790 --> 29:02.320
you will live a smooth life.

29:02.400 --> 29:03.130
All the best!

29:03.310 --> 29:04.400
All the best!

29:30.340 --> 29:34.350
♪ When the net of destiny
blocks the light ♪

29:34.730 --> 29:37.060
♪ Floating in the trap ♪

29:39.020 --> 29:40.710
♪ It's like a mystery ♪

29:42.260 --> 29:46.310
♪ But with the ending not yet determined ♪

29:46.700 --> 29:49.340
♪ No one can define me ♪

29:51.060 --> 29:53.020
♪ My whole life ♪

29:54.030 --> 29:57.150
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

29:57.370 --> 30:00.200
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

30:00.310 --> 30:01.310
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

30:01.330 --> 30:04.890
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

30:06.130 --> 30:07.640
♪ Do not speak to me
of what's inappropriate ♪

30:07.670 --> 30:09.130
♪ I am the moral order ♪

30:09.370 --> 30:12.170
♪ The gleam of the blade
tempers feathers into a phantom Phoenix  ♪

30:12.400 --> 30:13.350
♪ And these Phoenix bones of mine ♪

30:13.370 --> 30:18.340
♪ Empower me
to pierce through the wind and waves ♪

30:19.670 --> 30:21.400
♪ Allow me ♪

30:21.430 --> 30:24.030
♪ To not linger in shame,
to not give way ♪

30:24.380 --> 30:26.920
♪ To not be faithless,
to not admit defeat ♪

30:27.350 --> 30:30.240
♪ A body of stubborn pride
rises to shout that I ♪

30:30.310 --> 30:32.900
♪ Was never a creature
meant for the shallows ♪

30:33.290 --> 30:34.430
♪ Allow me ♪

30:34.600 --> 30:36.000
♪ To never pause ♪

30:36.280 --> 30:37.430
♪ Allow me ♪

30:37.660 --> 30:39.020
♪ To dare to shatter my bones ♪

30:39.310 --> 30:48.730
♪ Wherever I stand,
I dare to write a legend of glory ♪

31:00.080 --> 31:03.070
♪ Standing in the hurricane,
watching the fire rise ♪

31:03.340 --> 31:06.130
♪ Dancing on the blade's edge, I thread
through blood, writing my wild ode ♪

31:06.370 --> 31:07.290
♪ I am not one of the gentle ones ♪

31:07.340 --> 31:10.880
♪ How could my thoughts
be tethered to the soft begonia?  ♪

