37:22.390 --> 37:24.810
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

37:26.380 --> 37:29.850
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

37:30.280 --> 37:33.790
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

37:34.360 --> 37:37.330
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

37:37.800 --> 37:39.700
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

37:39.910 --> 37:41.520
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

37:41.850 --> 37:43.600
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

37:43.800 --> 37:45.970
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

37:44.550 --> 37:45.550
Will you marry me?

37:46.400 --> 37:49.550
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

37:47.290 --> 37:49.420
I've been your consort from the start.

37:49.850 --> 37:51.350
Now, I am your empress.

37:50.370 --> 37:52.790
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

37:51.630 --> 37:53.030
That's Yu Wanyin and Xiahou Dan.

37:52.850 --> 37:53.960
♪ Still unchanged ♪

37:54.030 --> 37:54.780
As Zhang San,

37:54.390 --> 37:57.290
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

37:57.280 --> 37:57.920
I want to ask you once more.

37:57.880 --> 37:59.340
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

37:59.410 --> 38:03.930
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

38:00.890 --> 38:01.820
Ms. Wang Cuihua,

38:03.320 --> 38:04.380
will you marry me?

38:11.320 --> 38:13.450
Whether it's Wang Cuihua or Yu Wanyin,

38:14.820 --> 38:16.400
inside the book or out,

38:17.810 --> 38:18.570
I do.

38:18.320 --> 38:21.840
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

38:22.400 --> 38:25.340
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

38:25.850 --> 38:27.780
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

38:27.970 --> 38:29.630
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

38:29.940 --> 38:31.600
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

38:31.930 --> 38:34.030
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

38:34.420 --> 38:37.640
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

38:38.380 --> 38:40.820
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

38:40.890 --> 38:41.950
♪ Still unchanged ♪

38:42.460 --> 38:45.340
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

38:45.870 --> 38:47.320
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

38:47.400 --> 38:54.780
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

39:10.710 --> 39:15.000
Happy birthday to you!

39:15.000 --> 39:20.000
Happy birthday to you!

39:20.550 --> 39:21.080
How is it?

39:21.190 --> 39:21.790
Is it good?

39:21.880 --> 39:22.810
It's delicious.

39:23.500 --> 39:24.560
Buy more next time.

39:25.150 --> 39:25.480
Okay.

39:25.840 --> 39:30.070
Happy birthday to you!

39:31.010 --> 39:32.210
Good job, my darling!

39:33.990 --> 39:35.670
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

39:42.740 --> 39:44.600
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

39:58.310 --> 39:59.020
How are you?

40:03.480 --> 40:04.210
I'm fine.

40:05.190 --> 40:05.790
Thank you.

40:07.410 --> 40:08.080
And you?

43:01.360 --> 43:03.620
Zhang San's Diary.

43:21.070 --> 43:21.870
Your Majesty.

43:23.070 --> 43:25.470
Concubine Yu,
who is to attend to you today,

43:25.710 --> 43:26.570
seems a bit odd.

43:27.140 --> 43:30.200
Her makeup and attire
are vastly different from usual.

43:35.400 --> 43:36.330
What do you mean?

43:37.190 --> 43:38.480
Your Majesty instructed that

43:38.480 --> 43:39.760
if a concubine scheduled to attend to you

43:39.760 --> 43:41.280
appears different from usual,

43:41.280 --> 43:42.280
we must report it.

43:47.670 --> 43:48.590
Concubine Yu.
